@Node Jokers "Wildcards"

	@{u}@{b}The wildcards@{ub}@{uu}



	Searcher don't manage AmigaDOS wildcards. There are now two wildcards : the "|" and "*" characters.

	| : It's equivalent to : OR.

	* : replace any field of characters. Attention : it's only enable while the option is active.


Example :
*mod*|*.8svx : search all files which contain "mod" and all files ended by the ".8svx" extension. 

@Endnode

